  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Enforcement of Operation Brock: guide for drivers of cross-Channel heavy goods vehicles (HGVs)
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Information for HGV drivers on routes, restrictions and possible fines in place during Operation Brock.</p>

  </div>
